<rss version="2.0" xmlns:dc="http://purl.org/dc/elements/1.1/"><channel><title>彭博加密货币</title><link>https://bloomberg.com/crypto/</link><description>彭博加密货币</description><lastBuildDate>Fri, 27 Mar 2026 01:13:57 GMT</lastBuildDate><generator>rfeed v1.1.1</generator><docs>https://github.com/svpino/rfeed/blob/master/README.md</docs><item><title>中东动荡加剧，比特币面临 140 亿美元期权到期</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-26/bitcoin-faces-14-billion-options-expiry-while-middle-east-turmoil-mounts</link><description>比特币今年最大的期权到期正与地缘政治波动相冲突，地缘政治波动没有显示出放松迹象，和平谈判的成败也不确定。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iFsaijb3rEV4/v2/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 16:55:29 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-26/bitcoin-faces-14-billion-options-expiry-while-middle-east-turmoil-mounts</guid></item><item><title>为了稳定币的可靠性，加密货币风投正在放弃 Web3</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-26/crypto-vcs-are-abandoning-web3-for-the-dependability-of-stablecoins</link><description>金融管道是吸引风投投资加密货币的原因。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iexkq.SsWdbI/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 21:00:01 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/newsletters/2026-03-26/crypto-vcs-are-abandoning-web3-for-the-dependability-of-stablecoins</guid></item><item><title>Saylor表示零售业拥有Strategy高收益证券80%的股份</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-26/michael-saylor-says-retail-own-80-of-strategy-s-high-yielding-preferred-shares</link><description>散户投资者显然还没有放弃迈克尔·塞勒 (Michael Saylor) 的梦想，即让比特币成为卓越的价值储存手段。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iataR.FPvUqo/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 19:16:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-26/michael-saylor-says-retail-own-80-of-strategy-s-high-yielding-preferred-shares</guid></item><item><title>加密货币通过符合 FNMA 资格的贷款进入抵押贷款市场</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-26/crypto-enters-the-mortgage-market-via-fannie-mae-eligible-loans</link><description>加密货币正在深入美国金融体系——这一次是通过抵押贷款市场。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/i5NvLZHuAyhA/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Thu, 26 Mar 2026 13:10:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-26/crypto-enters-the-mortgage-market-via-fannie-mae-eligible-loans</guid></item><item><title>币安在崩溃批评后收紧做市规则</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-25/binance-tightens-market-making-rules-in-wake-of-crash-criticism</link><description>全球最大的加密货币交易所币安 (Binance) 在 10 月份市场崩溃期间对数字资产市场做法提出批评后，正在收紧对该平台上的代币发行者和流动性提供者的规则。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iBEjkjyVrqRk/v1/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 18:38:52 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-25/binance-tightens-market-making-rules-in-wake-of-crash-criticism</guid></item><item><title>英国因存在干扰风险而禁止政治加密货币捐赠</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-25/uk-should-ban-crypto-donations-to-political-parties-review-says</link><description>英国政府宣布暂停以加密货币进行政治捐赠，并对海外选民的礼物设置上限，部长们试图遏制外国金融干预英国政治的风险。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/impmHx8XE9.c/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 12:39:37 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-25/uk-should-ban-crypto-donations-to-political-parties-review-says</guid></item><item><title>随着市场崩盘动摇信心，币安对加密货币的控制放松</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-25/binance-s-grip-on-crypto-loosens-as-market-crash-rattles-faith</link><description>币安控股有限公司曾经对加密货币交易的控制程度在传统市场中是不可想象的。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/iH6LpTpV0E5A/v3/1200x-1.png" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 13:27:16 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-25/binance-s-grip-on-crypto-loosens-as-market-crash-rattles-faith</guid></item><item><title>琼斯表示，澳大利亚央行将数字代币的关注重点从“如果”转向“如何”</title><link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-25/rba-shifting-focus-on-digital-tokens-from-if-to-how-jones-says</link><description>澳大利亚央行助理行长布拉德·琼斯表示，澳大利亚央行已将重点从批发数字代币是否会在金融体系中发挥作用转向如何实施，因为它希望在试点项目后释放效率收益。 &lt;br&gt;&lt;img src="https://assets.bwbx.io/images/users/iqjWHBFdfxIU/igoogbybOI3s/v0/1200x-1.jpg" alt="图像" /&gt;</description><pubDate>Wed, 25 Mar 2026 02:40:00 GMT</pubDate><guid isPermaLink="true">https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2026-03-25/rba-shifting-focus-on-digital-tokens-from-if-to-how-jones-says</guid></item></channel></rss>